c2pa:ingredientAssertionV3 a owl:Class ;
    rdfs:label "ingredientAssertionV3"@en ;
    rdfs:comment "Ingredient assertion (v3) (c2pa.ingredient.v3). CDDL: ingredient.cddl ingredient-map-v3. When the ingredient is a C2PA asset, activeManifest and validationResults are both required (validation is performed to determine the active manifest)."@en ;
